data.description: This Gorgeous Home is Situated in the Georg Ranch Community and is Conveniently Located Near Loop 1604, I-35, Natural Bridge Caverns and Plenty of Shopping and Dining. You will be Welcomed with A Meticulously Maintained Lot w/ Mature Trees and Landscaping Lights. As You Enter Through the Double Doors into a Grand Entry, Marvel at the Large Living Area, Perfect for Relaxing in the Open Layout in Front of the Cozy Fireplace, Private Home Office, and a Formal Dining Space w/Neutral Color Palette. Wood Flooring & Ceramic Tile Through-out.  The Chef if Your Family Will Appreciate the Large Kitchen Which is the Heart of the Home with Lots of Custom Cabinetry, Double Oven, and a Breakfast Bar Which Serves 6.  Off the Kitchen You Will Find the Convenient Oversized Laundry Room w/ Sink & Large Utility Closet.  Your Master Suite is Tucked Away for Privacy and Features Natural Light Filtering Through an Abundance of Windows, a Spa-Like Bathroom w/Split Vanities, Walk-in Shower, Garden Tub and a Walk-in Closet w/Built-In Dresser.   After a Long Day, Venture Outside and Enjoy a Closed-In Sunroom w/Professional Window Tinting as Well as A Covered 13x22 Patio in Backyard Under Huge Oaks All Surrounded by a Privacy Fence and Sprinkler System. Recent Updates Include the Roof Which Was Replaced in 2019, and Quarterly Septic Maintenance, Energy Saving Heat-Blocking Window Screens and Outdoor Termite Bait System.   Entertain Kids 14x17 Enclosed Sunroom/Play Area.  You will find Extra Storage in the 3-Car Garage and Attic Area in House. Please Don't Miss the Opportunity to Make This Your Home!
